title: Joan of Paris (1942)
description:
A barmaid named Joan (Michele Morgan) sacrifices her own safety to help five fugitive British airmen escape from France. From the time the airmen make their rendezvous with a British agent in a Paris church, they become the desperate quarry of the unrelenting Nazi Gestapo. Taut suspense holds you to the harrowing conclusion of this wartime drama.
